title: The Majesty of New Orleans (Architecture Art Ebook).pdf
description:
pdf / English / 120 pages / 22 MB / 1992

Paul and Lee Malone, husband and wife, also collaborated on Louisiana Plantation Homes: A Return to Splendor, The Majesty of the River Road, The Majesty of the Felicianas, The Majesty of New Orleans, The Majesty of the Garden District, and The Majesty of the Garden District Postcard Book, all published by Pelican. In each, Paul provided the stunning photography of interiors and exteriors, and Lee has written the historical background.

*****

More photos than words, but very nice. It is divided into four sections: architecture, coutryards & patios, Ironworks, and cemeteries. I wish it had been longer than the 112pp. And that it included some of the stunning Protestant churches of New Orleans. The bibliography lists just seven works! But a nicely packaged, well illustrated book.
